obo:ECO_0001225  a  owl:Class .

gomodel:SYNGO_457  a      owl:Ontology ;
        rdfs:comment      "Rationale: Increased paired-pulse facilitation in parallel fiber-Purkinje cell synapses in Munc13-3 knockout mice.\n\n25/4/2017 Pim\n- Although Munc13-1 is a known SV priming protein, I agree with annotation to the more broad term \"SV exocytosis\" for Munc13-3 since this data does not allow to resolve \"docking\", \"priming\", and \"fusion\".\n- Because of the known role of Muc13-1 in priming, I do not select the \"regulates...SV exocytosis\" option for Munc13.3. Experimental description: For the generation of a Munc13-3 targeting vector, we used genomic clones pMunc13-3/13 and pMunc13-3/14 (isolated from a 129SVJ mouse genomic library in λFIX II; Stratagene, La Jolla, CA), which contain multiple exons of the murine Munc13-3 gene." ;
        lego:modelstate   "production" ;
        dc:contributor    "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-0755-5899" , "https://orcid.org/0000-0003-3185-5709" , "https://orcid.org/0000-0003-0938-8534" , "https://orcid.org/0000-0001-7351-8706" ;
        dc:date           "2017-04-26" ;
        dc:title          "SYNGO_BP_457" ;
        pav:providedBy    "https://syngo.vu.nl" ;
        biolink:in_taxon  "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/NCBITaxon_10090" .

